    "For example, clinicians should be aware of both the distinct inflammatory [18] and infectious sinusitis [19,20] as well as the numerous odontogenic]or dental treatment-related causes of ODS [6,21].",
    "Since ODS has not been highlighted adequately in otolaryngologic or dental therapeutic guidelines, non-ODS experts may not be aware of some of these diagnostic and therapeutic nuances [6,22,23].",
